import React, { useEffect, useRef } from 'react'; import Chart from 'chart.js/auto'; import { MdRefresh, MdAddCircle, MdReceiptLong, MdShoppingCart, MdCreditCard, MdPieChart, MdAccountBalanceWallet, MdVpnKey, MdTask, MdEdit, MdSettings, MdDashboard } from 'react-icons/md'; // Material Design Icons const DashboardPage: React.FC = () => { const categoryExpenseChartRef = useRef(null); const chartInstance = useRef(null); // Geçici veri tanımları (Backend'den gelmesi gereken veriler) const category_expenses = [ { category_type: 'Gıda', total_amount: 500 }, { category_type: 'Ulaşım', total_amount: 150 }, { category_type: 'Eğlence', total_amount: 200 }, { category_type: 'Fatura', total_amount: 300 }, { category_type: 'Diğer', total_amount: 100 }, ]; const recent_transactions = [ { type: 'expense', description: 'Market Alışverişi', date: '2025-07-25', amount: 350 }, { type: 'income', description: 'Maaş', date: '2025-07-24', amount: 8000 }, { type: 'expense', description: 'Online Sipariş', date: '2025-07-23', amount: 420 }, { type: 'income', description: 'Freelance Ödeme', date: '2025-07-22', amount: 2500 }, ]; useEffect(() => { if (categoryExpenseChartRef.current) { if (chartInstance.current) { chartInstance.current.destroy(); // Önceki chart instance'ı yok et } const ctx = categoryExpenseChartRef.current.getContext('2d'); if (ctx) { const labels = category_expenses.map(item => item.category_type); const data = category_expenses.map(item => item.total_amount); const colors = [ '#FF6384', '#36A2EB', '#FFCE56', '#4BC0C0', '#9966FF', '#FF9F40', '#FF6384', '#C9CBCF' ]; chartInstance.current = new Chart(ctx, { type: 'doughnut', data: { labels: labels, datasets: [{ label: 'Toplam Harcama', data: data, backgroundColor: colors, borderColor: '#fff', borderWidth: 2, hoverOffset: 4 }] }, options: { responsive: true, maintainAspectRatio: false, plugins: { legend: { position: 'bottom', labels: { padding: 20, usePointStyle: true, font: { size: 12 } } }, tooltip: { callbacks: { label: function (context) { const value = context.parsed; const total = context.dataset.data.reduce((a, b) => a + b, 0); const percentage = ((value / total) * 100).toFixed(1); return `${context.label}: ₺${value.toLocaleString('tr-TR')} (${percentage}%)`; } } } }, animation: { animateScale: true, animateRotate: true } } }); } } }, [category_expenses]); const refreshDashboard = () => { alert('Dashboard yenileniyor...'); // Basit bir bildirim // Gerçek uygulamada burada API çağrısı veya state güncellemesi yapılabilir window.location.reload(); // Sayfayı yeniden yükle }; return (
